INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS:

    <Place holder for actual install directions>

SERVER SETUP:

	Apache Instructions:
		* Enable mod_rewrite
		* Use the included .htaccess files
	
	nginx Instructions:
		* Use ProxyPass to an internal Apache server handling your site
		or
		* Use the following under your site's location directive in virtual.conf
		example:
			location / {
				root   <full path to arcane>;
				index  index.php index.html index.htm;
				if (-f $request_filename) {
					break;
				}
				rewrite . index.php last;
			}

	IIS, Lighttpd, and all other web servers:
		* You're on your own.